rule: overdue_invoice
severity: amber
surfaces: dashboard,invoices
text: Invoice INV-2026-01 is 9 days overdue. Send a reminder to Contoso GmbH.
cta: Send reminder | invoicing.sendReminder | {invoice_id=inv-123}

rule: recurring_invoice_draft_waiting
severity: teal
surfaces: dashboard,invoices
text: Recurring invoice draft for Fabrikam Ltd is ready for 2026-08-01.
cta: Open draft | navigate:/invoices/draft-456 | {}

rule: dla_overdrawn_bik
severity: amber
surfaces: dashboard,dla
text: Your loan account is -£1,500.00 overdrawn. The Isle of Man has no UK-style s455 charge, but an interest-free loan can create a taxable benefit in kind - charge interest at the official rate or clear it with a dividend.
cta: Clear with dividend | navigate:/dividends?amount=150000 | {}

rule: filing_deadline_window
severity: amber
surfaces: dashboard,reports
text: VAT return due 2026-07-30 - file with Isle of Man Customs & Excise.
cta: Open filing calendar | reports.openFilingCalendar | {}

rule: dividend_set_aside
severity: teal
surfaces: dashboard,dividends
text: Set aside £150.00 personally for IoM income tax if you declare the available £1,500.00 dividend headroom.
cta: Open dividends | dividends.open | {}

rule: rates_stale
severity: amber
surfaces: banking,dashboard,invoices
text: ECB rates are stale. Refresh rates before issuing or settling foreign-currency transactions.
cta: Refresh rates | moneyfx.refreshRates | {}

rule: company_minimum_directors
severity: amber
surfaces: dashboard,settings
text: Your company is registered under the Companies Act 1931 and must have at least 2 directors - profile lists 1.
cta: Open company settings | navigate:/settings/company | {}
